Package com.hhstechgroup.tests.regressionBaseline.iii_GroupEnrollment

This Package contains test classes covering all the test stories for Group Enrollments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GroupEnrollmentRetroActiveRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This test class verifies the submission of a retroactive adjustment Group enrollment.
    GroupProviderAppealApprovalProcessTest
    This test class verifies approving the appeal of a denied Group enrollment.
    GroupProviderAppealDenialProcessTest
    This test class verifies denying the appeal of a denied Group enrollment.
    GroupProviderApproveEnrollmentTest
    This test class changes the status of a Group enrollment from 'Pending Review' to 'Approved'.
    GroupProviderCoCProcessAppealDenialTest
    This test class verifies denying the appeal of a denied Group CoC.
    GroupProviderCocProcessTest
    This test class verifies the submission and approval of a Group Address Details CoC, and verifies the error messages displayed when the creation of a Group Ownership CoC or a Group Program Participation CoC is attempted.
    GroupProviderDenyCoCProcessTest
    This test class verifies the submission and denial of a Group Identifying Information CoC.
    GroupProviderDenyEnrollmentTest
    This test class changes the status of a Group enrollment from 'Pending Review' to 'Denied'.
    GroupProviderPaymentFeeVerificationTest
    This test class verifies the submission of a Group enrollment with In-State payment fee verification and a Group enrollment with Out Of State payment fee verification.
    GroupProviderPreConditionSetupTest
    This test class sets the Systems Option configuration for Group Provider.
    GroupProviderReactivationTerminationTest
    This test class verifies the changing of a Group enrollment status from 'Reactivated' to 'Terminated'.
    GroupProviderRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This test class verifies the submission of a Group enrollment.
    GroupProviderRetroActiveAdjustmentApprovalTest
    This test class verifies the Group Provider enrollment span.
    GroupProviderRevalidationVerification
    This class contains a method to do revalidation through API, a Group provider completes the revalidation, Then gets submitted by an internal user.
    GroupProviderSubmitScreeningTest
    This test class verifies changing the status of a Group enrollment from 'Under Screening' to 'Pending Review'.
    GroupProviderSuspensionReactivationTest
    This test class changes the status of a Group enrollment from 'Active' to 'Suspended', then reactivates the enrollment.
    GroupProviderVerifyDocumentReviewTest
    This test class verifies the Group enrollment 'Document Review' status.
